\p 
\v 19 Pe mo gangɨɨ¹in gajúin¹ Herodes gacɨ́ɨ¹ɨ Sé³ fu Egipto do joon gajnéi¹ jaain²¹ ángel tya' Ña'ñʉ'¹ʉ' 'in jin'² sɨɨ'²¹ɨ 'ii:
\p 
\v 20 ―Ráan²un, cweei'¹ tee¹e xuui²¹² coon'¹³ sáa³a fu Israel tsʉ nijúun²mo 'in 'iin²¹²in ijngaai'² 'ii.
