\v 5 Mo gangalíin tsá² tya' Jesús lɨ' ngoo'¹³ tyíia¹ lɨ' ca taain²¹² do niga'iin²mo‑tsi coon²¹on 'iñi'¹.
\v 6 Joon Jesús gajin'²in sɨɨ'²¹ɨ 'ido:
