\v 41 La joon jon gaungøø¹i 'in tyʉ'² to² tya' untsá² coon'¹³ 'in tɨfo'² tya' ley coon'¹³ tsá² fariseos coon'¹³ tsacøøi'¹³. Joon sɨ́ɨ²i la 'oo'²¹ 'ii jin'²in:
\p 
\v 42 ―Gaun'láai² 'ino tsá² xeei'²¹ pe jo lí² láa¹i 'ña'a. Wana la jai'² 'ii Rǿøi¹³ tya' tsá² Israel cwoxáa¹i tsaa' crúu¹³ no joon iun'goo²o' 'ii.
\v 43 Tsaa'¹‑tsi 'in tsañʉʉ'¹ no Dios jin'²in, né²du' wana 'iin²¹²in Dios 'ii joon 'e láa¹i 'ido 'ii tsʉ gajin'²in 'e Jóon¹ Dios 'ii.
