\v 55 Do‑o teein¹ tsamɨ́² fúui¹ wíin²gɨxʉ jǿø²ø. Nigangɨ¹ 'in tsamɨ́² do coon'¹³ Jesús fu Galilea joon nigaunjíi²in Jesús.
\v 56 Joon jee²¹² do sin'² María Magdalena coon'¹³ María sáa³ Jacobo coon'¹³ José. Sin'²mo jon in sáa³ jóon¹ Zebedeo do.
