\v 57-58 Capii'³ teein¹gɨ jmɨɨ²¹² joon mo gangó¹ jaain²¹ tsá² sá² cuu² seein²¹ fuu²¹ Arimatea 'in sii²¹ Sé³. Gango¹ 'ido tyani Pilato, ngamɨɨ¹ɨ cuerpo tya' Jesús. 'Ii jaain²¹ tsá² 'in tsaa'¹‑tsi Jesús.
\v 59 Joon gaxíia² cuerpo tya' Jesús joon gacɨɨn'¹³in coon²¹ 'mɨ'² taa²¹ 'e tyʉ́².
\v 60 'In Sé³ do natyʉ'² to² 'e nalɨ́¹ coon²¹ 'aan¹ tya'a tsaa' xá¹ 'e tsa'ii²¹ mi júun²in pe gatan'²mo Sé³ Jesús tsi 'aan¹ 'mɨ́ɨ² do. Joon² mo ngayuui'¹³ gataan'¹in Jesús do joon gajnii²o 'oo²¹ too²¹ 'aan¹ do coon'¹³ coon²¹ cuun²¹² fee'¹ 'áai¹. Joon gangaa'¹³mo mo ngayuui'¹³ do.
\v 61 Pe do‑o née¹i María Magdalena coon'¹³ 'in María jaain²¹gɨ do co' do.
\s1 Ngalíin² 'láa² nga'aa²a 'aan¹ tya' Jesús
